long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Game Description
Jump LOVES to jump on stacks of bricks! Be the ULTIMATE stack jumper and quickly jump on top of the stacks as they are built. But watch out, if you miss your jump, you will tumble all they way down to the ground! Ouch!

You can also play other Categories Game.

Be a top player, and you will earn another jumper to jump on stacks. Good luck!

Game Instructions
Tap or click to Play. Tap Jump to jump on each stack of bricks as they zip to the stack. Be quick or your miss your jump and tumble to the ground!

Gain points and be the ULTIMATE stack jumper! Good luck!
